title: FM Einheit - Sensation Death (Electronic/Synth/Music for dance)
description:
F.M. Einheit - Sensation Death (1997) @ 320 kbps

Re-seed. Difficult to describe this music. It&#039;s a kind of electronic/synthesizer music for a kind of ballet. Does remind me of old German electronic sounds (i.e. Kraftwerk, DAF, Klaus Schulze).

Visit http://www.invisiblerecords.com/aotw/index.htm for more information.

Hope the files stay healthy this time.

Download, listen, seed, and if you like it, purchase the original. These bands are worth it (IMHO).

Enjoy & seed!
